Title: Why package by feature first and then by layer?
Why disallow package within the class name?
Description: Motivation After opening a directory it is the developers job to filter out the files that are not relevant to their task at hand. The more words to filter, the more difficult it becomes to quickly orient themselves and start making changes. Disallowing package within the class name promises to reduce this information overload.

Title: Why prefer unit testing through layer entrypoints?
Description: Status Quo There is significant artistic variance on how to craft tests which provide developers quick and useful feedback.
